Check_MK Plugin to check hardware health of HP Proliant Servers per agent:

    The client plugin will return various stats about server health.
    
    The script was tested on the following Debian versions: Squeeze
    
    Any feedback welcome, DM to michael[at]mgeb[dot]org. I'm also reading the english
    check_mk ML: checkmk-en@lists.mathias-kettner.de


// INSTALLATION INSTRUCTIONS

    On your Check_MK clients:
    
        Install the following debian packages:
            * cciss-vol-status
            * hp-health
        
        Copy plugins/hp_proliant_agent to your clients into /usr/lib/check_mk_agent/plugins/
    
    On your Nagios Server:
    
        Copy checks/hp_proliant_agent to your server into /usr/local/share/check_mk/scripts/

